### Version
3.1.1

### Reproduction link
[https://codesandbox.io/s/vue-template-5rovy](https://codesandbox.io/s/vue-template-5rovy)







### Steps to reproduce
```js
actions: {
    test() {
      let prom = new Promise((resolve) => {
        setTimeout(function(){
          resolve("DONE"); 
        }, 3000);
      });
      prom['id'] = 10
      console.log(prom) // Object contains id
      return prom;
    }
  }
```
```js
created() {
    let pf = this.$store.dispatch("test");
    console.log("PF", pf); // No id property
    pf.then(res => {
      console.log(res);
    });
  }
```

### What is expected?
The properties of the object should be displayed in the console.

### What is actually happening?
The properties of the object are ignored.

